			text="Chapter 2: Engage your community">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="This chapter helps you begin the community engagement process that will provide the foundation for your work in ERB. This chapter guides you through considerations for community engagement such as creating connections and building and maintaining relationships. This community engagement process will be important to completing the next ERB chapters.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="There are three potential steps in Chapter 2:">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="1. ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Underlined"
			text="Identify and diagram your community connections.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="2. ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Underlined"
			text="Create a Community Engagement Plan.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="3. ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Underlined"
			text="Reflection.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=" Each chapter concludes with reflection prompts to check in and take stock.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Depending on what information you already have on hand, here are the routes you can take:">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;- If you haven't done any community engagement yet, we recommend that you work through all Ch. 2 activities step-wise, starting ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="here"
			linkType="internalActivity"
			link="21">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;- If you need to update, expand, or identify gaps in your existing community network, begin with a community connections diagram ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="here"
			linkType="internalActivity"
			link="22">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;- If you are already well connected with your community, begin with the community engagement planning process ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="here"
			linkType="internalActivity"
			link="23">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;&#x9;- If you want to learn more about the importance of equity-informed community engagement, click ">
